com.interpss.core.aclf.hvdc

Interface BaseConverter<TBus extends BaseAclfBus<?,?>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BusRef<TBus>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ThyConverter<TBus>, VSCConverter<TBus>, VSCConverterDyn
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseConverterImpl, ThyConverterImpl, VSCConverterDynImpl, VSCConverterImpl

    public interface BaseConverter<TBus extends BaseAclfBus<?,?>>
extends BusRef<TBus>
    A representation of the model object 'Base Converter'. HVDC VSC Converer

    The following features are supported:

    • Parent Hvdc
    • Converter Type
    • Ref Bus Id
    See Also:
    HvdcLinePackage.getBaseConverter()
